gg2list                 Convert a ggplot to a list.
group2NA                Drawing ggplot2 geoms with a group aesthetic is
                        most efficient in plotly when we convert groups
                        of things that look the same to vectors with
                        NA.
layer2traces            Convert a layer to a list of traces. Called
                        from gg2list()
paramORdefault          Convert ggplot params to plotly.
plotly                  Main interface to plotly
plotly-package          A R API for plot.ly
set_config_file         Set keyword-value pairs in Plotly config file
set_credentials_file    Set the keyword-value pairs in Plotly
                        credentials file
show_config_file        Read and print Plotly config file, wrapping
                        get_credentials_file()
show_credentials_file   Read and print Plotly credentials file,
                        wrapping get_credentials_file()
signup                  Sign up to plotly.
toFill                  Use default ggplot colour for fill (gray20) if
                        not declared
toRGB                   Convert R colours to RGBA hexadecimal colour
                        values
